
'''''The First Grader''''' ni filime yikinamico ya biografiya ya 2010 iyobowe na Justin Chadwick<ref>https://unric.org/en/the-first-grader/</ref> . Irimo Naomie Harris, Oliver Litondo, na Tony Kgoroge<ref>https://www.spiritualityandpractice.com/films/reviews/view/20874</ref> . Iyi filime ishingiye ku nkuru y'impamo ya Kimani Maruge<ref>https://www.nytimes.com/2011/05/13/movies/the-first-grader-justin-chadwicks-tale-of-kenyan-culture-review.html</ref>, [[Kenya|umuhinzi wo muri Kenya]] wiyandikishije mu mashuri abanza afite imyaka 84 nyuma yaho guverinoma ya Kenya yatangaje ko amashuri abanza ari buntu ku isi mu 2003<ref>https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-reviews/first-grader-film-review-29951/</ref>. 

