=== Gufata amashusho ===
[[Dosiye:Africa6_006.jpg|right|thumb| Ikibaya kinini cya Rift muri Kenya, ahabereye amashusho.]]
Producer ukomoka muri Amerika witwa Sam Feuer yasanze inkuru kurupapuro rwambere rwa LA Times ahitamo  We<ref>https://www.theguardian.com/global-development/2011/jun/19/kenya-first-grader-education</ref>, hanyuma, ashaka umufatanyabikorwa Richard Harding<ref>https://www.wikiwand.com/en/The_First_Grader</ref>, yafatanije na BBC Films maze aha akazi Ann Peacock kwandika amashusho. Filime yakozwe n’abongereza yafatiwe  ahitwa Rift Valley muri Kenya, nubwo mbere byavuzwe ko izafatirwa muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika yepfo]] <ref>https://www.commonsensemedia.org/movie-reviews/the-first-grader</ref>. Umuyobozi Chadwick yagize ati: "Twashoboraga kuyirasa muri Afurika y'Epfo, ariko Kenya ifite izo mbaraga zidasanzwe, zidasobanutse zirangwa mu bana, ndetse n'abantu twakoraga film". <ref>https://www.helpage.org/blogs/sarah-marzouk-10/the-first-grader-a-real-life-example-of-age-helps-196/</ref>

